üéØ CCEE QUICK REVISION POINTS
Diffie-Hellman = Key Exchange (not encryption)
No authentication ‚Üí MITM possible
Vernam (OTP) = Perfect secrecy
DES weak due to 56-bit key
Triple DES = slower but stronger than DES
Cryptool = concept visualization tool
